{"tid":1822450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"吸引多d人去黃店的方法","createTime":"2020-01-13T03:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T06:05:23.000Z","uid":205927,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f79ca0981ddbb01745a51037fb78fa882a0318cc","tid":1822450,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"依兩日成日係到嘈影大頭～不如諗下點吸引多d人去黃店仲好。<br />\n拋磚引玉～<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 黃店優惠券</span><br />\n簡間講就係派優惠券比人吸引多d人去黃店，但黃店已經幫左手足咁多，仲出優惠券我怕d人會冇錢賺，所以我覺得 可以眾籌， <span style=\"color: pink;\">成立良心商店基金，係果到 分一批錢出嚟搞優惠券</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 藍店取代app</span><br />\n雖然現在有好多黃店app,但香港人真係好賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得可以<span style=\"color: pink;\">出個app,輸入你想去的店or想買的物品，當然係藍店，就根據 食物種類，提供最近最相似的取代品比你</span><br />\n<br />\n大家仲有冇咩題議？"},{"pid":"70615b77422530c4d4840e439083ba59cfea441d","tid":1822450,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"有冇辦年貨攻略，介紹黃店既小冊子 etc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198bdacd36f53451ac756d8ce945488ed93b98ed","tid":1822450,"uid":51583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:45:08.000Z","msg":"唔關價錢問題<br />\n其實明顯有部份人已經降低左罷食意欲<br />\n諗下點推番高大家個士氣先有用"},{"pid":"cb6833ce0bd984fe7b7a25784f97c3aadcc383c3","tid":1822450,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"仲有情人節攻略，父親節攻略"},{"pid":"2f269051fa6f48fa12ebc365d7ff7802f383cbe2","tid":1822450,"uid":205927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70615b77422530c4d4840e439083ba59cfea441d","tid":1822450,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"有冇辦年貨攻略，介紹黃店既小冊子 etc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"之前好似見到有，講去邊到買花同 買盆菜"},{"pid":"c182a9321797c7dd83f71d405cc9fa51f